init_text:
Once upon a time there was an old mother pig who had one hundred little pigs and not enough food to feed them. So when they were old enough, she sent them out into the world to seek their fortunes. You know the story about the first three little pigs. This is a story about the 92nd little pig.

The 92nd little pig built a house out of depleted uranium. And the wolf was like, "dude."

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the wolf couldn't blow it down, because depleted uranium is one of the most dense elements in the known universe!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: (except for the neutron star material in his teeth)

actions.text: (except for the neutron star material in his teeth)

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So he had to come up with a new plan.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He disguised himself as a health inspector, and he walked up to the house and just stood there for a while.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Then, he knocked on the door and said, "Little pig, little pig!

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The 92nd little pig recognized his voice, so he said, "No thanks, wolf.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I must have the wrong address.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the wolf knew that the little pig would go to visit his neighbor, so he waited outside the next house.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And as soon as the 92nd little pig walked out, he snuck up and put a bag over his head and took him away.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The wolf put the 92nd little pig in a big pot and started to heat the water.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But the 92nd little pig was smart.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He managed to squirm his way to the edge of the pot, and when he did, he grabbed a nearby radio antenna and pulled it out.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The antenna was attached to the city's radio station, and when he pulled it out, all of the city's residents could hear him screaming for help

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: So the people of the city stormed the wolf's house and rescued the 92nd little pig.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And when the 92nd little pig got home, he wrote a book called "How to Build an Igloo Out of Uranium" which became

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: And he lived happily ever after.
